WEBVTT

00:02.559 --> 00:06.519
Torchwood, outside the government,
beyond the police.

00:06.554 --> 00:08.845
Tracking down alien life on earth,

00:08.880 --> 00:11.884
arming the human race
against the future.

00:11.919 --> 00:15.040
The 21st century is when
everything changes...

00:15.075 --> 00:16.484
and you've got to be ready.

00:16.519 --> 00:20.999
This programme contains
some strong language.

00:22.000 --> 00:28.074
